19:09.680 --> 19:11.350
if we make money from this investment,

19:11.350 --> 19:12.770
I can marry you.

19:12.880 --> 19:13.610
Thank you for

19:13.680 --> 19:16.310
helping me raise enough betrothal money
for my mom.

19:16.310 --> 19:18.160
Let me go! Let me go!

19:18.920 --> 19:19.590
Let me go!

19:21.590 --> 19:22.440
Trying to escape?

19:22.440 --> 19:23.170
How dare you!

19:23.200 --> 19:24.460
Realize your mistake?

19:24.920 --> 19:25.510
Stop it!

19:25.550 --> 19:26.110
Master Bei.

19:26.110 --> 19:27.590
Master Bei, I'm sorry.

19:27.590 --> 19:30.440
I'll never try to run again.
I know I was wrong.

19:30.440 --> 19:32.000
Tell them to stop hitting me.

19:32.000 --> 19:33.100
During your chats,

19:34.440 --> 19:36.510
will you still ask them
to call the police for you?

19:36.510 --> 19:37.720
No more calling the police.

19:37.720 --> 19:40.550
I won't call the police anymore.

19:41.400 --> 19:42.030
Master Bei.

19:42.030 --> 19:42.600
Sir,

19:42.830 --> 19:44.690
Master Bei said we're ready to go.

19:44.960 --> 19:45.440
Got it.

19:55.680 --> 19:56.340
Master Bei.

19:57.030 --> 19:57.560
Brother.

20:06.350 --> 20:07.220
Good girl.

20:08.680 --> 20:09.590
Just this once.

20:09.590 --> 20:10.420
OK, OK.

20:10.550 --> 20:12.680
It hurts a lot to be beaten, doesn't it?

20:12.750 --> 20:15.460
I'll help you
not to make mistakes again, OK?

20:15.590 --> 20:16.550
OK, OK.

20:16.590 --> 20:17.750
Thank you, Master Bei.

20:17.750 --> 20:19.610
-Thank you, Master Bei.
-Be good.

20:42.880 --> 20:45.010
This is the price of talking nonsense.

20:49.030 --> 20:50.310
Don't think you can mess around

20:50.310 --> 20:51.480
just because I'll be away for a few days!

20:51.480 --> 20:52.230
Get to work!

21:30.540 --> 21:39.070
[School of Atmospheric & Oceanic Sciences,
Lihai University of Science & Technology]

21:30.720 --> 21:31.580
Hello, Ms. Yan.

21:35.400 --> 21:35.960
It's me.

21:37.110 --> 21:38.970
Did Officer Li contact you later?

21:39.180 --> 21:43.830
[Lihai Meteorology]

21:39.350 --> 21:39.920
No.

21:40.680 --> 21:42.590
After that Ouyang got arrested,

21:42.590 --> 21:44.120
he didn't contact me again.

21:44.550 --> 21:47.160
What did Officer Li say about the video?

21:47.480 --> 21:49.730
He said it will be strictly sealed off,

21:50.160 --> 21:51.070
but...

21:51.260 --> 21:56.070
[Lihai Meteorology]

21:53.480 --> 21:54.070
It's just...

21:54.070 --> 21:56.070
I-I heard those bastards say

21:56.160 --> 21:58.160
they might package the video

21:58.160 --> 21:59.680
and sell it to porn sites.

22:00.030 --> 22:01.840
B-But it's just a possibility.

22:01.960 --> 22:02.920
They couldn't have

22:02.920 --> 22:04.380
had the time to do all that.

22:04.830 --> 22:06.290
Did you contact Fang Fang?

22:08.880 --> 22:09.510
No.

22:12.000 --> 22:12.790
I'm sorry.

22:14.350 --> 22:15.880
Why are you saying sorry?

22:15.920 --> 22:17.750
This is what I wanted to do.

22:18.480 --> 22:19.550
Even if it wasn't for you

22:19.550 --> 22:20.510
or Leilei,

22:21.070 --> 22:21.960
just as a man,

22:21.960 --> 22:23.480
I couldn't just watch those scumbags

22:23.480 --> 22:24.880
exploit women like that.

22:25.030 --> 22:25.880
Lu.

22:26.750 --> 22:27.440
Lu?

22:27.690 --> 22:32.260
[Lihai Meteorology]

22:28.160 --> 22:29.680
Alright, don't overthink it.

22:29.680 --> 22:30.740
I have things to do.

22:31.000 --> 22:31.400
Bye.

22:38.680 --> 22:39.200
Dr. Luo.

22:39.960 --> 22:40.760
Your package.

22:41.160 --> 22:41.760
Thank you.

22:43.830 --> 22:44.890
Are you busy today?

22:45.550 --> 22:46.030
Not bad.

22:46.590 --> 22:47.070
Not bad.

22:51.200 --> 22:51.680
Hello?

22:52.960 --> 22:54.090
I'll be right there.

23:24.310 --> 23:25.830
Jiale! Jiale!

23:32.110 --> 23:33.370
Fasten your seatbelt.

23:42.880 --> 23:44.190
[Incoming call: Dr. Luo Liang]

23:46.070 --> 23:47.400
Not answering the call?

23:50.160 --> 23:51.180
[Incoming call: Dr. Luo Liang]

23:51.210 --> 23:53.830
[Dr. Luo Liang]

23:53.200 --> 23:53.600
Hello?

23:55.000 --> 23:55.480
Ms. Yan.

23:57.640 --> 23:58.970
I received the clothes,

23:59.400 --> 24:00.660
but there's a problem.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.270
What problem?

24:05.400 --> 24:06.260
I was wondering

24:06.550 --> 24:08.310
why you didn't just give them to me

24:08.310 --> 24:09.370
in person instead.

24:12.070 --> 24:14.200
I've been quite busy with work lately.

24:14.840 --> 24:17.400
Does that mean
Jiale hasn't been eating properly again?

24:17.400 --> 24:19.350
I recently saw a tutorial
for making cold rice noodles.

24:19.350 --> 24:20.270
It requires washing the dough.

24:20.270 --> 24:21.330
I want to practice.

24:21.620 --> 24:23.160
Whenever you and Jiale have time—

24:23.160 --> 24:24.440
I'm sorry, Dr. Luo.

24:25.510 --> 24:26.740
It's almost the end of the term.

24:26.740 --> 24:28.770
Jiale and I are really busy.

24:31.030 --> 24:31.480
I see.

24:32.880 --> 24:34.140
I-I'm driving right now.

24:34.140 --> 24:35.120
I'll hang up now.

24:35.830 --> 24:37.110
OK, bye.

24:37.290 --> 24:38.230
[Dr. Luo Liang]

24:38.340 --> 24:39.230
[Missed call: Dr. Luo Liang]

24:47.070 --> 24:48.880
What happened between you two?

24:50.830 --> 24:51.880
What do you mean?

24:54.000 --> 24:55.820
Dr. Luo just helped you

24:55.960 --> 24:57.160
and lent you clothes.

24:57.350 --> 24:58.080
But just now,

24:58.480 --> 24:59.720
you talked to him on the phone

24:59.720 --> 25:01.200
like it was a scam call.

25:02.110 --> 25:03.710
I don't think I was that rude.

25:04.400 --> 25:05.190
You were.

25:05.720 --> 25:07.850
You didn't treat him like this before.

25:39.750 --> 25:40.610
Oh my goodness.

25:41.200 --> 25:42.350
I just went to the restroom

25:42.350 --> 25:44.080
and saw that Madam Chen is back.

25:45.070 --> 25:46.240
You mean the hypochondriac?

25:46.240 --> 25:46.830
Yes, her.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.720
Every time, she brings a suitcase

25:49.720 --> 25:51.160
full of scans and medical records.

25:51.160 --> 25:54.160
And she always insists that
I read them from beginning to end.

25:54.160 --> 25:55.220
Every single time.

25:56.000 --> 25:56.720
She alone can drive

25:56.720 --> 25:58.240
the other waiting patients crazy.

25:58.240 --> 25:59.970
I've been working all morning,

26:00.640 --> 26:02.150
and I've only seen 8 patients.

26:02.150 --> 26:03.210
If she comes again,

26:04.000 --> 26:06.330
how am I supposed to
see my other patients?

26:07.440 --> 26:08.900
Why don't you take a break?

26:09.060 --> 26:10.150
I'll cover for you.

26:12.650 --> 26:14.020
I love a challenge.

26:15.590 --> 26:16.030
OK.

26:16.230 --> 26:16.830
Thanks.

26:35.660 --> 26:36.480
Where are we?

26:38.160 --> 26:39.200
Should be there soon.

26:39.200 --> 26:41.130
We've passed the boundary marker.

27:04.960 --> 27:05.290
Here.

27:15.590 --> 27:16.000
Here.

27:27.000 --> 27:27.530
Brother!

27:28.240 --> 27:28.640
Here.

27:39.830 --> 27:42.310
He Dayong! He Xiaobing! Lin Huosheng!

27:42.610 --> 27:43.790
How did the word get out?

27:43.790 --> 27:45.250
We are Lihai Police!

27:45.550 --> 27:46.550
Damn that Yu Kexin.

27:46.550 --> 27:49.280
You are suspected of a crime
and are surrounded!

27:49.960 --> 27:50.920
Drop your weapons

27:50.920 --> 27:52.170
and surrender!

27:52.240 --> 27:53.780
It's your only way out!

27:53.880 --> 27:54.670
Fire!

27:54.880 --> 27:55.400
Fire!

28:05.480 --> 28:05.960
Fire!

28:06.600 --> 28:07.820
Fire! Fire!

28:15.240 --> 28:15.840
Watch out!

28:19.950 --> 28:21.300
Pudge, are you OK?

28:25.680 --> 28:27.530
The bullet hit his right shoulder blade.

28:27.530 --> 28:28.640
It's not a penetrating injury.

28:28.640 --> 28:30.300
He is not in immediate danger.

28:31.550 --> 28:32.200
Thank you.

28:38.920 --> 28:41.650
You're leaving
just because the doctor has left?

28:41.760 --> 28:43.160
You're so cold-blooded.

28:44.510 --> 28:45.350
I told you to sit out

28:45.350 --> 28:46.070
the arrest operation,

28:46.070 --> 28:47.400
but you wouldn't listen.

28:47.400 --> 28:48.530
With your physique,

28:48.590 --> 28:50.830
you're defintely
not suited for field duty.

28:50.830 --> 28:51.310
What?

28:54.750 --> 28:55.080
Here.

28:55.880 --> 28:56.660
Careful.

28:58.920 --> 29:00.450
So what if I'm not suited?

29:01.350 --> 29:03.000
At least I'm thick enough.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.530
If it were someone else,

29:05.240 --> 29:08.100
the bullet would have
gone through them and hit you.

29:08.310 --> 29:09.400
You desk officers

29:09.400 --> 29:10.750
have no combat experience

29:10.750 --> 29:12.280
and don't know your limits.

29:14.070 --> 29:14.800
Does it hurt?

29:16.200 --> 29:18.930
A little,
now that the anesthesia is wearing off.

29:26.830 --> 29:27.480
Thank you.

29:30.790 --> 29:31.920
I said, "Thank you."

29:35.640 --> 29:36.570
You're welcome.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.400
Paw Patrol,

29:39.790 --> 29:40.240
you can't

29:40.240 --> 29:41.790
just say thanks.

29:43.070 --> 29:44.800
You have to take actual action.

29:48.720 --> 29:49.480
What action?

30:04.830 --> 30:06.440
Don't push your luck.

30:09.810 --> 30:10.610
Lin Huosheng,

30:12.150 --> 30:13.480
let me interrogate him.

30:17.350 --> 30:18.660
Focus on your recovery

30:19.070 --> 30:20.600
and return to the team soon.

30:23.510 --> 30:24.770
What do you want to eat?

30:25.480 --> 30:26.590
Canned yellow peaches.

30:26.590 --> 30:27.000
OK.

30:27.960 --> 30:29.000
Skewers, hot pot,

30:29.000 --> 30:30.860
iced Coke, fried chicken, fried—

30:30.880 --> 30:32.150
You're on a roll, huh?

30:38.310 --> 30:40.110
Why ask if you won't let me order?

30:43.270 --> 30:44.750
Anti-fraud is a required course.

30:44.750 --> 30:46.680
Build a solid defense
and fulfill your duty.

30:46.680 --> 30:50.010
Lihai Must-See, taking you
to the forefront of anti-fraud.

30:50.240 --> 30:50.810
Recently,

30:50.700 --> 30:51.970
[Exit Gate]

30:51.110 --> 30:52.110
a special fraud case

30:52.110 --> 30:53.590
occurred in our city.

30:53.420 --> 30:55.690
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

30:53.830 --> 30:54.830
The criminals used

30:54.830 --> 30:56.880
phones, WeChat, and other platforms

30:56.880 --> 30:58.760
to quickly get close to the victim

30:58.830 --> 31:00.050
and establish a romantic relationship.

30:58.870 --> 31:01.150
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:00.270 --> 31:03.350
Then, they repeatedly used investment
and wealth management as an excuse

31:03.350 --> 31:05.880
to extort over one million yuan
from the victim,

31:05.880 --> 31:07.440
resulting in serious consequences.

31:07.440 --> 31:08.090
As such,

31:07.550 --> 31:11.440
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:08.160 --> 31:11.490
we interviewed the renowned psychologist
Professor Tian.

31:12.070 --> 31:14.350
Scams conducted
through romantic relationships

31:14.350 --> 31:16.430
are, firstly, highly covert.

31:17.030 --> 31:19.640
Victims often don't take the initiative
to mention it to their family and friends,

31:19.250 --> 31:22.190
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:20.030 --> 31:22.430
thus missing the opportunity to be warned.

31:22.640 --> 31:23.480
Secondly,

31:23.920 --> 31:26.510
victims usually experience
a tremendous sense of shame

31:26.510 --> 31:27.350
and loss.

31:26.580 --> 31:28.470
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:27.720 --> 31:28.960
Such emotional distress

31:28.960 --> 31:31.750
will seriously damage the victims'
physical and mental health,

31:31.750 --> 31:32.210
[Ms. Yan, I caught Xia Yi.
I caught him myself.]

31:31.790 --> 31:33.790
even leading to suicidal thoughts.

31:34.270 --> 31:35.120
[Officer Li]

31:35.290 --> 31:36.970
[Ms. Yan, I caught Xia Yi.
I caught him myself.]

31:35.790 --> 31:37.550
Recently, this new type of scam

31:37.640 --> 31:38.830
has been occurring frequently.

31:38.830 --> 31:40.160
Under the guise of romance,

31:39.000 --> 31:43.120
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:40.350 --> 31:42.010
they induce victims to invest

31:42.070 --> 31:43.400
and defraud them of their money.

31:43.400 --> 31:45.200
They are organized
with a division of labor,

31:45.200 --> 31:47.480
and conduct professional training
in PUA speaking skills

31:45.510 --> 31:47.250
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:47.550 --> 31:49.030
for emotional manipulation.

31:49.030 --> 31:50.370
This training of theirs

31:49.510 --> 31:51.790
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:50.430 --> 31:52.330
is under the guise of
teaching people how to date.

31:52.330 --> 31:54.720
They turn the entire process of
hitting on someone, getting to know them,

31:54.620 --> 31:57.870
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

31:54.720 --> 31:55.790
to having relations

31:55.790 --> 31:56.830
into a standardized procedure

31:56.830 --> 31:59.090
that can be quickly replicated.

31:59.550 --> 32:02.690
They also have this
reward and punishment system.

32:02.010 --> 32:04.650
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

32:02.880 --> 32:04.720
The number of TDs...

32:04.790 --> 32:07.700
TD, that is takedown,
means getting someone into bed.

32:07.700 --> 32:09.440
They take the number of people
you sleep with

32:09.440 --> 32:10.880
as the performance metric.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.160
They even encourage trainees

32:12.160 --> 32:14.750
to record the process
of getting victims into bed

32:12.190 --> 32:14.220
[Lihai Must-See]
[At the forefront of anti-fraud]

32:14.960 --> 32:17.020
and upload such lewd pictures online

32:17.270 --> 32:19.080
to prove their achievements.

32:19.440 --> 32:22.110
I feel that throughout this whole process,

32:22.310 --> 32:24.920
some moral boundaries are being crossed.

32:25.000 --> 32:26.330
I also want to

32:26.960 --> 32:28.370
remind the viewers

32:28.400 --> 32:32.150
that if you feel
you have had a similar experience,

32:32.430 --> 32:34.400
you can go to the relevant institutions

32:34.400 --> 32:36.160
to find out more.

32:40.580 --> 32:43.220
[Ms. Yan, I caught Xia Yi.
I caught him myself.]

32:41.480 --> 32:41.940
Ms. Yan,

32:42.480 --> 32:43.340
I caught Xia Yi.

32:43.680 --> 32:44.810
I caught him myself.

32:44.830 --> 32:47.160
To actively respond to
and crack down on this phenomenon,

32:47.160 --> 32:48.110
our station has now

32:48.110 --> 32:49.440
opened a victim hotline.

32:49.440 --> 32:50.790
If you or your family and friends

32:50.790 --> 32:51.830
have experienced similar

32:51.830 --> 32:54.350
financial fraud
disguised as a romantic relationship,

32:54.350 --> 32:56.440
you can use the contact information
at the bottom of the screen

32:56.440 --> 32:57.960
or follow our station's Weibo account

32:57.960 --> 32:59.760
to receive
psychological and legal assistance,

32:59.760 --> 33:01.820
and also provide us with more clues.

33:02.680 --> 33:06.160
I expect them to be available at all times
to answer my phone.

33:06.400 --> 33:07.160
You're up.

33:08.110 --> 33:09.710
I want first-class service.

33:11.640 --> 33:13.040
I have the best investor.

33:14.160 --> 33:15.620
Just tell them what I said.

33:15.790 --> 33:17.080
And no bullshit.

33:17.270 --> 33:18.070
Don't give in,

33:18.160 --> 33:18.710
OK?

33:19.240 --> 33:19.840
That's it.

33:24.880 --> 33:25.880
Have some coffee.

33:29.410 --> 33:31.760
Don't interrupt when I'm on a work call.

33:34.830 --> 33:35.240
Right.

33:36.240 --> 33:37.510
We'll go to Chang'an Building first,

33:37.510 --> 33:39.240
then drop me off at the company.

33:40.640 --> 33:41.510
Chang'an Building?

33:41.510 --> 33:42.840
Are we picking up Mr. Li?

33:44.200 --> 33:46.400
I don't like people prying into my work.

33:47.070 --> 33:49.070
Didn't you say
I'm your personal assistant?

33:49.070 --> 33:49.960
I want to share

33:49.960 --> 33:52.160
some of the burden regarding your work.

33:52.240 --> 33:55.700
"Personal assistant" means
you assist with my personal life.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.110
Work is not included.

33:58.830 --> 34:00.040
So to you,

34:00.550 --> 34:01.550
I am just

34:01.880 --> 34:02.620
your boy toy,

34:03.240 --> 34:04.830
plus a free driver,

34:05.200 --> 34:07.000
bodyguard, and bag carrier.

34:07.270 --> 34:07.870
Is that it?

34:10.760 --> 34:11.980
I know you're trying

34:12.110 --> 34:13.370
to make me feel guilty.

34:13.840 --> 34:14.469
Too bad,

34:15.110 --> 34:16.750
your PUA tricks

34:16.920 --> 34:17.850
don't work on me.

34:22.070 --> 34:23.190
Do you need to reconsider

34:23.190 --> 34:24.250
our relationship?

34:25.550 --> 34:27.880
I can call my driver
to pick me up right now.

34:35.670 --> 34:36.190
Bitch!

34:39.550 --> 34:40.530
Controlling your emotions

34:40.530 --> 34:42.659
is the first step to becoming an adult.

34:53.870 --> 35:00.110
[Beloved daughter Jian Leilei]

34:55.480 --> 34:56.219
Leilei.

34:57.840 --> 34:59.600
You can rest in peace now.

35:00.480 --> 35:01.030
Yan Ling

35:02.110 --> 35:05.020
found the scammers who harmed you.

35:06.360 --> 35:08.150
They will never be able

35:08.150 --> 35:10.300
to harm other girls again.

35:12.630 --> 35:14.740
But my baby girl...

35:16.230 --> 35:18.460
can never come back.

35:24.830 --> 35:27.780
[Beloved daughter Jian Leilei]

35:31.760 --> 35:32.490
Uncle, Aunt,

35:33.030 --> 35:33.670
I'm sorry.

35:34.460 --> 35:35.920
What are you sorry for?

35:37.670 --> 35:38.870
If it weren't for you,

35:40.230 --> 35:42.580
how could Leilei's name be cleared?

35:45.920 --> 35:47.720
When I was at my most vulnerable,

35:49.030 --> 35:50.800
you and Leilei saved me.

35:52.140 --> 35:54.200
But when Leilei needed help the most,

35:56.190 --> 35:57.710
I failed to protect her.

35:58.760 --> 36:00.570
Please don't say that.

36:02.190 --> 36:03.840
Leilei doesn't blame you.

36:03.130 --> 36:05.580
[Beloved daughter Jian Leilei]

36:08.270 --> 36:10.530
If her spirit in heaven

36:10.840 --> 36:12.070
knows this outcome,

36:13.190 --> 36:15.000
she will feel at peace.

36:21.960 --> 36:24.490
You haven't had time
to visit your mom, right?

36:24.760 --> 36:26.960
Take these dried sweet potatoes to her.

36:27.400 --> 36:29.500
We dried these ourselves.

36:29.710 --> 36:30.840
They're delicious.

36:31.190 --> 36:32.000
This is too much.

36:32.000 --> 36:33.330
She can't finish it all.

36:34.370 --> 36:35.620
[Incoming call: Dr. Luo Liang]

36:35.110 --> 36:37.480
Is it your mom calling to rush you?

36:40.230 --> 36:41.890
Alright, we're heading back.

36:41.960 --> 36:42.480
Let's go.

36:42.480 --> 36:43.240
Drive safely.

36:43.240 --> 36:44.140
OK, thanks.

36:54.360 --> 36:54.760
Hello?

36:55.550 --> 36:57.210
I'm downstairs at your place.

36:57.840 --> 36:58.920
I'm not home.

36:59.150 --> 37:00.400
I went back to my hometown for something.

37:00.400 --> 37:01.860
Then I'll wait for you here

37:01.920 --> 37:03.050
until you come home.

37:58.670 --> 37:59.550
I saw the news.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.520
So you don't need me anymore.

38:07.920 --> 38:08.510
What?

38:09.760 --> 38:12.220
I've thought it through
these past few days.

38:12.230 --> 38:13.040
To you,

38:13.880 --> 38:15.920
I'm just a free therapist.

38:17.710 --> 38:20.510
When Jian Leilei and Li Changning
were in trouble,

38:20.670 --> 38:22.000
you happened to meet me.

38:23.150 --> 38:24.210
You needed me then.

38:26.030 --> 38:27.450
Like a drowning person

38:27.920 --> 38:28.880
needing a rope.

38:31.670 --> 38:33.530
But now that things are resolved,

38:34.590 --> 38:35.550
you feel like

38:36.280 --> 38:37.540
you need to go back to

38:37.590 --> 38:40.050
becoming the calm and independent teacher.

38:40.430 --> 38:42.630
So of course you no longer need the rope.

38:42.890 --> 38:43.900
That's not true.

38:44.790 --> 38:45.230
I...

38:45.630 --> 38:46.110
It's OK.

38:47.820 --> 38:48.690
Even so,

38:51.250 --> 38:52.580
I still want to thank you

38:53.670 --> 38:55.070
for choosing to trust me,

38:57.020 --> 38:58.230
for telling me so much

38:59.630 --> 39:00.840
about your private

39:02.390 --> 39:03.650
and painful memories.

39:06.690 --> 39:07.640
And thank you

39:09.260 --> 39:10.740
for comforting me so much

39:15.160 --> 39:16.690
when my father passed away.

39:23.250 --> 39:23.860
And

39:24.920 --> 39:26.980
for letting me meet the lovely Jiale.

39:34.270 --> 39:35.260
But the two of us

39:37.110 --> 39:38.710
can't go on like this.

39:41.520 --> 39:43.790
If you want to heal through therapy,

39:45.510 --> 39:46.400
I can't do it.

39:47.730 --> 39:49.460
I have my professional ethics.

39:50.440 --> 39:51.500
Towards a patient,

39:51.620 --> 39:54.350
I must remain completely
neutral and objective,

39:54.840 --> 39:56.640
without any personal feelings.

39:57.740 --> 39:58.720
But towards you,

40:09.680 --> 40:11.010
I can't do that anymore.

40:18.320 --> 40:20.520
When I held you at the hospital that day,

40:22.550 --> 40:24.410
I became very sure of my feelings.

40:27.150 --> 40:27.800
But later,

40:27.800 --> 40:28.840
I could also feel

40:29.880 --> 40:31.540
you gradually drifting away.

40:33.360 --> 40:33.800
Love

40:34.960 --> 40:36.010
or healing?

40:37.030 --> 40:38.620
We made different choices.

40:45.230 --> 40:45.850
Yan Ling.

40:47.010 --> 40:48.160
I sincerely suggest

40:50.030 --> 40:51.230
that you find

40:51.230 --> 40:52.760
a professional therapist.

40:53.950 --> 40:56.080
Otherwise, if your exposed old wounds

40:56.600 --> 40:58.060
are not properly treated,

40:59.760 --> 41:00.570
I'm worried

41:01.960 --> 41:03.620
you'll get hurt again,

41:04.580 --> 41:07.040
and it'll also affect
the people around you.

41:15.470 --> 41:16.630
Anyway,

41:20.210 --> 41:21.870
I want to say a proper goodbye.

41:25.280 --> 41:26.160
From now on,

41:29.570 --> 41:30.830
I wish you all the best.

42:06.440 --> 42:10.830
[The Dark Romance]

42:32.820 --> 42:35.210
[Support group
for victims of romance fraud]

42:35.360 --> 42:38.800
[Verification mode enabled
by the group chat admin]

42:36.230 --> 42:36.800
Hello.

42:37.430 --> 42:39.880
I'm also a victim of
a pig butchering scam.

42:38.820 --> 42:43.680
[Please state why
you want to join the group]

42:40.760 --> 42:43.320
I really hope you can help me.

42:43.790 --> 42:44.550
Thank you.
